Assignment 3 README

This project implements brain state classification from fMRI data for two datasets:
1. sub-01/ses-test
2. sub-01/ses-retest

For each dataset, preprocessing, brain masking, feature extraction, optional PCA,
classification, K-fold cross-validation, and parameter search were performed independently.

